Dungeon Crawl is a game about slaying monsters using fun combat and having satisfying character progression

-- Creating multiple characters --
Rename the file "playerFile" to something else. i.e. playerFile1 (a better way would be to use the character's name)
Create a new .txt fil with the name "playerFile"
Run game
# This will run you through character creation and save that character to the new file
if you want to resume your old progress change the old files name back to playerFile
and be sure to change the name of the file you were just running

# Weapon Abilities #
Lifesteal - returns hp on hit
Sharp Edges - chance to deal bonus damage

# gear ability #
Negate - has a chance to completely negate damage